            <a name="section2"></a>
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Financial Status Overview<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 feature-visual d-md-none">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/savings.jpg" alt="Financial Status Image">
          </div>          
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <p class="lead">
              To purchase or build a suitable facility for the meditation centre in a location where there is permission for Religious Assembly, it takes about a minimum investment of 1.5 million dollars. Towards this, we can put about $500,000 by selling the current house and also obtain loan of about $300,000 from the bank. This still leaves a <span class="font-weight-bold">shortfall of about $700,000</span>. 
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
              To cover the shortfall, we have established a Meditation Centre Development Fund and started obtaining pledges from our devotees and well wishers. Contributions made to this fund will solely be used for the establishment of the new meditation centre facility. We kindly request the generous people in Edmonton, across Canada and the World, to come forward and assist us in this difficult situation. 
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 feature-visual d-none d-md-block">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/savings.jpg" alt="Financial Status Image">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

