            <a name="section3"></a>
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Development Fund Contributions<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 d-md-none" style="text-align:center;">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto feature-visual" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/projectlogo.png" alt="Fund Contributions Image" style="width:340px;">
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-7">
            <p class="lead">
              Your generosity is the only source of funding available to save this meditation centre. Please help this meritorius deed and inform your commitment by email to <a href="mailto:president@abva.org">president@abva.org</a> or by contacting the Meditation Centre at 780-641-9795.
            </p>
            <p class="lead"> 
              As a registered, charitable, non-profit organization, we will provide <span class="font-weight-bold">Official Tax Receipts</span> for your donation. You may use the <a href="http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/chrts-gvng/dnrs/svngs/clmng1b2-eng.html" target="_blank"><span class="font-weight-bold">Charitable Donation Tax Credit Calculator</span></a> of the Canada Revenue Agency to see how much tax credit you will be entitled to receive based on total annual charitable donations you make.
            </p>
          </div>
